1. Zamalo* nisam zaboravio da je danas rođendan mog prijatelja. (I almost forgot it was my friend's birthday today.)
2. On je zamalo* izgubio živce. (He almost lost his temper.)
3. Kažu da su zamalo* izgubili bitku. (They say they almost lost the battle.)
4. Zamalo* me nisu uhapsili. (They almost arrested me.)
5. Nisam zamalo* zaspao na sastanku. (I almost didn't fall asleep at the meeting.)